# Map .goop files for GitHub Linguist.
#
# Goop is not in github-linguist/linguist yet — see docs/github-linguist/README.md
# for the submission package. Until that PR merges, F# gives reasonable highlighting
# for match/let/ADTs (approximate, not Goop-accurate).
#
# After Linguist merge, replace with:
#   *.goop linguist-language=Goop linguist-detectable=true

*.goop linguist-language=F# linguist-detectable=true
